# Laravel AI Harness

This project uses {{ package_name }}.

Before editing harness-managed files, prefer changing package configuration or source templates, then run:

```bash
php artisan ai-harness:update
```

Generated blocks and generated files are package-owned. Keep project-specific notes outside managed blocks.
